00036 #include "integral_tria6.h"
00037 
00038 int intH_tria6(const unsigned int FLAG, double X[6][3], double *Xeval, 
00039                double *Int, double *normal)
00040 {
00041     const unsigned int NODES_IN_ELEM = 6;
00042     unsigned int i, j;
00043     double A, B, C, dx, dy, dz, J, nxdx, rsq, W;
00044     double L[2], N[6], XL[3];
00045 
00046     /* Initialize */
00047     if(!FLAG) for(i = 0; i < NODES_IN_ELEM; i++) Int[i] = 0.0;
00048     else for(i = 0; i < 18; i++) Int[i] = 0.0;
00049 
00050     /* Integrate using Gauss-Legendre quadrature */
00051     for(i = 0; i < TNGAUSS; i++){
00052         L[0] = TGauss[i][0];
00053         L[1] = TGauss[i][1];
00054         W = TGauss[i][2];
00055 
00056         /* Shape functions N and Jacobian J for these (L1,L2) values */
00057         shape_tria6(L,N);       
00058         J = X2L_tria6(X,XL,L,N);
00059 
00060         /* Auxiliar quantities */
00061         dx = Xeval[0] - XL[0];
00062         dy = Xeval[1] - XL[1];
00063         dz = Xeval[2] - XL[2];
00064         rsq = dx*dx + dy*dy + dz*dz;
00065         A = J*W/pow(rsq,1.5);
00066 
00067         /* Add contribution for each node in this element */
00068         if(!FLAG){
00069             nxdx = dx*normal[0] + dy*normal[1] + dz*normal[2];
00070             A = A*nxdx;
00071             for(j = 0; j < NODES_IN_ELEM; j++) Int[j] -= A*N[j];
00072         }
00073         else{
00074             C = A*dz;
00075             B = A*dy;
00076             A = A*dx;
00077             for(j = 0; j < NODES_IN_ELEM; j++){
00078                 Int[j*3] += A*N[j];
00079                 Int[j*3+1] += B*N[j];
00080                 Int[j*3+2] += C*N[j];
00081             }          
00082         }
00083     }
00084 
00085     return 0;
00086 }
